The lady weekend is an annual upbeat business lifestyle and personal growth event powered by Aisha Abu Bakr with an aim to educate, embolden and inspire women in the creative sector. As women, we have a better understanding of our needs and wants.,this birthed the recreational ambience for effective communication between creative entrepreneurs., established and emerging with government organizations, finance institutions, and investors.  Our ethos is to inspire every woman in technology, fashion, and the art sector who attends ‘The Lady Weekend’. This year’s tag line is THE FINISHER, this is to round up all that has been implemented in women owned businesses in the last quarter of the year. Business development, Marketing, Strategic execution, Financial discipline are key areas that we focus on leading women to meet their business and personal goals. Loads of SHOPPING, GAMES AND MUSIC  too